meta.name: Knative Performance Tests-Template
meta.description: template created from dashboard: Knative Performance Tests

queries.text:
from(bucket: "knative-serving")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "Knative Serving load test")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "requests")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["flavor"] == "zero")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: last, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "last")

from(bucket: "knative-serving")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "Knative Serving load test")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "latency-min")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["flavor"] == "zero")
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with _value: r._value / 1000.0 / 1000.0}))
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

properties.note:
#### Load test results
* Zero = Only hook the activator in at zero
* Always = Always hook the activator in.
* 200 = Hook the activator in until we reach 200 concurrent requests

properties.note:
#### Dataplane probe results
* Deployment = Vanilla k8s Deployment
* Activator = Always hook the activator in
* Queue = Only hook the activator in when scaled to zero.
